headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Discounts
content:
Looking to legitimize your operation with all the corporate bells and whistles? Executive Offices — along with all their Renovations — are half off, while Vehicle Warehouses are 30% off. Plus, there’s a collection of vehicles available on sale:

- Pfister 811 – 40% off
- Dewbauchee Seven-70 – 40% off
- B-11 Strikeforce – 35% off
- Benefactor Stirling GT – 40% off

And more! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
